{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_03_01",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 アメリカ留学",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう！　ですわ！　{user}さん！\n今日はよく晴れた気持ちのいい天気ですわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san!\nIt’s a nice‚ clear sunny day today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、すず。今日はいつにも増して元気だな\n何かいいことでもあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Morning‚ Suzu. You’re in even better spirits than normal today.\nDid something good happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "実は……怜の悩みをこの私が華麗に解決したのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I’ve neatly solved the problem of Rei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "怜がお父様と絶縁状態だという話は\n{user}さんもご存じですわね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did {user}-san know that Rei and\nher father are estranged?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "私もその話を聞いて、なんとかしなければと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And since knowing that‚ I thought I have to do something…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルがいかに素晴らしい職業か\n怜の実家に乗り込んでお父様に説教したのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I went to where Rei’s parents lived and explained to her father\nwhat a great job it is to be an idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "そんな私の活躍もあって、怜とお父様のわだかまりが\n少しだけ解消されたんですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And what I did helped to break down\nsome of the barrier between Rei and her father!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すずが実家に乗り込んだって聞いた時は驚いたよ\nうまくいってよかったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was shocked when I heard you just went into her parents’ house‚ Suzu.\nI’m glad it went so well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "やはり家族仲はいいに越したことはないですわね\n私もいいことをして晴れ晴れとした気分ですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s nothing better than good family relations.\nNow I’m in a wonderful mood because I did something good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言うすずは、最近ご家族とはどうなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since you say that‚ Suzu‚ how have things been with your family lately?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "相変わらずですわ\nお父様はともかく、お母様が厳しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Same old same old.\nFather’s not so bad‚ but Mom’s so strict…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すずのお父さんとはまだお会いしたことがないんだが\nどんな人なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve never met your father‚ Suzu.\nWhat’s he like?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "私が言うのもなんですが、娘に甘い人ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This might sound biased‚ but he’s kind to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "昔からほしいものはなんでも買ってくれて\nお小遣いに不自由したことはありませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He buys me anything I wanted.\nAnd I never asked for pocket money.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "すずの金銭感覚がずれているのはその頃からだったのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s when your financial sense got so messed up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "私がアイドルになることに反対していましたが\nグランプリ以降は変化があったみたいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He was against me becoming an idol‚\nbut he seems to have changed since the Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "最近は「うちの娘は世界一可愛いアイドルだ」と\n周囲に触れ回っているそうですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Recently he’s been going around telling people\n“Our daughter is the world’s cutest idol.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "実家の棚に私のCDやグッズ、生写真を飾って\nお客様が来るたびに自慢しているらしいですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s a shelf in the house decorated with my CDs‚ merchandise‚ and portraits.\nApparently he shows them off to anyone who visits.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "意外と親馬鹿なんだな……\nでも親子仲が悪い訳じゃなくて安心したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a surprisingly doting dad…\nI’m reassured to hear you don’t have a bad relationship with your parents.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわね\nお父様との仲はそこまで悪くありませんが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess so.\nMy relationship with my father isn’t so bad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "父親が甘い反動で、母親が厳しくなってしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when father spoils me‚ Mother reacts by getting stricter…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "私にアイドルを辞めさせようとして\n仕事現場に乗り込んで来たこともありましたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She even tried to make me quit being an idol\nby coming to where I was working.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あの時はすずを留学させようとしていたが\nそれは今も変わらないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At that time‚ she tried to make you study abroad‚\nbut is she still the same way?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "……そういえば最近は留学しろと言ってきませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Now that you mention it‚ she hasn’t been ordering me to study abroad lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "きっと私の活躍を見て、アイドルが私の天職だと\n分かってくださったに違いありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She must have been watching me work as an idol and\nrealized that I’m born to be one!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "だといいんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you say so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1233.3333334000258,
          "startTime": 164.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "大変ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is terrible!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに慌ててどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you in a panic?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
